trans-unit.source: Provides a standard set of component-related commands, which have predefined key input gestures and <see cref="P:System.Windows.Input.RoutedUICommand.Text" /> properties.
trans-unit.target: 提供標準的元件相關命令集，其含有預先定義的按鍵輸入動作和 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Input.RoutedUICommand.Text" /> 屬性。

trans-unit.source: The commands in the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands> class and commands in the other command library classes, such as <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.NavigationCommands>, are intended to represent a set of common commands that application programmers encounter frequently.
trans-unit.target: 中的命令<xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands>類別和其他命令命令程式庫類別，例如<xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands>和<xref:System.Windows.Input.NavigationCommands>，用於代表一組應用程式設計人員經常遇到的常見命令。

trans-unit.source: The commands only represent the instance of the <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand> and not the implementation logic for the command.
trans-unit.target: 命令只代表的執行個體<xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand>不實作邏輯的命令。

trans-unit.source: The implementation logic is bound to the command via a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.CommandBindings%2A>.

For example, if the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A> command is executed on a control (the command target), the logic that performs the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A> command may not be provided by the command target, so the application writer is responsible for writing the logic that determines how the command target handles the command.
trans-unit.target: 例如，如果<xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A>（命令目標），會執行的邏輯控制項上執行命令<xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A>命令可能無法提供命令目標，因此應用程式寫入器會負責寫決定的邏輯方式命令目標會處理命令。

trans-unit.source: Many controls do provide implementation logic, though, for many of the commands in the command library.
trans-unit.target: 許多控制項提供實作邏輯，不過，許多命令程式庫中的命令。

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> class provides logic for the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Paste%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Cut%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Copy%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Undo%2A> command, and <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Redo%2A> command.
trans-unit.target: 比方說，<xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox>類別會提供邏輯<xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Paste%2A>命令，<xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Cut%2A>命令，<xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Copy%2A>命令，<xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Undo%2A>命令，並<xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Redo%2A>命令。

trans-unit.source: See the class documentation for particular control classes for more information.
trans-unit.target: 請參閱特定控制項類別，如需詳細資訊的類別文件。

trans-unit.source: For more information on commands and commanding, see [Commanding Overview](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/commanding-overview.md).
trans-unit.target: 如需有關命令和命令的詳細資訊，請參閱[指揮概觀](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/commanding-overview.md)。
